# In the manner or style of a [[confession]].

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# {{italbrac|Roman Catholic church}} A small room where [[confession]] (the [[sacrament]] of reconciliation) is performed.  Traditional architecture has used three adjacent rooms separated by gratings with sliding doors; the priest hearing the conffessions sits in the middle room and alternately opens one of the doors to hear confession from the person kneeling on that side.

